featured_question.question: What is Juma Prayer time in this masjid?
featured_question.answer: Jumma Qutba Starts around 1:25 or 1:30 P.M onwards, Jumma Namaz around 1:40 / 1:45 P.M...  its better to be here by 1:00 P.M Arternoon, b'coz the Imam sab Bayaan is very attractive & beautifull to listen.
